
************************** Instructions To Run The Project ************************

Clone: git clone git@github.com:MuhammadAttiqueUrRehman/MentoryAssignment

Open Project directory and run command:

1- 'cd frontend && npm i && cd ..'
2- 'cd backend && composer install && cd ..'


Once packages are installed run following command: 

1- 'docker compose up --build'

When build success run migrations:
1- 'docker exec laravelapp php artisan migrate'

To Check running images:
1- 'docker ps -a'

 backend running on: http://localhost:8000
 
 frontend running on: http://localhost:3000/

